/*Query the two cities in STATION with the shortest and longest CITY names, as well as their respective lengths (i.e.: number of characters in the name). If there is more than one smallest or largest city, choose the one that comes first when ordered alphabetically.8?
(select CITY, char_length(CITY) as len_city from STATION order by len_city,city limit 1) union all (select CITY, char_length(CITY) as len_city from STATION order by len_city desc limit 1);
